onditions are met (1) the agreement does not expire within 1 year and is not cancelable by the lender except for violation of an objectively determinable provision, (2) no violation exists at the BS date, and (3) the lender has entered into the financing agreement is expected to be financially capable of honoring the agreement.'),(1714,'LineOfCreditFacilityAnnualPrincipalPayment',1,2,2,'Line of Credit Facility, Annual Principal Payment','Amount of decrease in debt under credit facility arrangement from principal payment.'),(1715,'LineOfCreditFacilityCommitmentFeeAmount',1,2,2,'Line of Credit Facility, Commitment Fee Amount','Amount of the fee for available but unused credit capacity under the credit facility.'),(1716,'LineOfCreditFacilityCurrentBorrowingCapacity',1,1,1,'Line of Credit Facility, Current Borrowing Capacity','Amount of current borrowing capacity under the credit facility considering any current restrictions on the amount that could be borrowed (for example, borrowings may be limited by the amount of current assets), but without considering any amounts currently outstanding under the facility.'),(1717,'LineOfCreditFacilityFairValueOfAmountOutstanding',1,1,1,'Line of Credit Facility, Fair Value of Amount Outstanding','Fair value of the amount outstanding under the credit facility.'),(1718,'LineOfCreditFacilityIncreaseAccruedInterest',1,1,2,'Line of Credit Facility, Increase, Accrued Interest','Increase for accrued, but unpaid interest on the credit facility for the period.'),(1719,'LineOfCreditFacilityIncreaseDecreaseForPeriodNet',1,1,2,'Line of Credit Facility, Increase (Decrease), Net','Amount of increase (decrease) of the credit facility.'),(1720,'LineOfCreditFacilityIncreaseDecreaseOtherNet',1,1,2,'Line of Credit Facility, Increase (Decrease), Other, Net','Amount of increase (decrease), classified as other, of the credit facility.'),(1721,'LineOfCreditFacilityInterestRateDuringPeriod',2,NULL,2,'Line of Credit Facility, Interest Rate During Period','T