e by the consolidated entity.'),(2557,'RealEstateInvestmentPartnershipCostOfSales',1,2,2,'Real Estate Investment Partnership Cost of Sales','Amount of cost of sales related to investments in real estate partnerships and variable interest entities.'),(2558,'RealEstateInvestmentPartnershipRevenue',1,1,2,'Real Estate Investment Partnership Revenue','Amount of revenue recognized from investments in real estate partnerships and variable interest entities.'),(2559,'RealEstateInvestments',1,2,1,'Real Estate Investments, Net','Amount of real estate investments, net of accumulated depreciation, which may include the following: (1) land available-for-sale; (2) land available-for-development; (3) investments in building and building improvements; (4) tenant allowances; (5) developments in-process; (6) rental properties; (7) other real estate investments; (8) real estate joint ventures; and (9) unconsolidated real estate and other joint ventures not separately presented.'),(2560,'RealEstateInvestmentsJointVentures',1,2,1,'Real Estate Investments, Joint Ventures','The book value of investments in real estate joint ventures including direct and indirect investments.'),(2561,'RealEstateOwnedAccumulatedDepreciation',1,1,1,'Real Estate Owned, Accumulated Depreciation','Amount of accumulated depreciation for real estate owned (REO).'),(2562,'RealEstateOwnedValuationAllowanceComponent',1,1,1,'Real Estate Owned, Valuation Allowance, Component','The valuation allowance loss on real estate owned or any impairment losses taken against real estate investments held for use or resale.'),(2563,'RealEstateOwnedValuationAllowance',1,1,1,'Real Estate Owned, Valuation Allowance','For each period for which an income statement is required, disclosure of the changes in the allowance, including balances at end of period.'),(2564,'RealEstateOwnedValuationAllowanceAmountsApplied',1,2,2,'Real Estate Owned, Valuation Allowance, Amounts Applied','Amount of the valuation allowance for real estate owned that was applied in the period against the carrying amount of real estate owned that was sold, written down or written off.'),(2565,'RealEstateInvestmentPropertyAtCost',1,2,1,'Real Estate Investment Property, at Cost','Amount of real estate investment property which may include the following: (1) land available-for-sale; (2) land available-for-development; (3) investments in building and building improvements; (4) tenant allowances; (5) developments in-process; (6) rental properties; and (7) other real estate investments.'),(2566,'RealEstateInvestmentPropertyNet',1,2,1,'Real Estate Investment Property, Net','Amount of real estate investment property, net of accumulated depreciation, which may include the following: (1) land available-for-sale; (2) land available-for-development; (3) investments in building and building improvements; (4) tenant allowances; (5) developments in-process; (6) rental properties; and (7) other real estate investments.'),(2567,'RecapitalizationCosts',1,2,2,'Recapitalization Costs','Amount of recapitalization costs for professional fees associated with restructuring debt and equity mixture that do not qualify for capitalization.'),(2568,'ReceivableForRecoveryOfImportDutiesNet',1,2,1,'Receivable for Recovery of Import Duties, Net','Carrying amount as of the balance sheet date of tariffs due either from customers or suppliers arising from sales or purchases, or as previously overpaid to tax authorities or vendors.'),(2569,'ReceivablesFromCustomers',1,2,1,'Receivable from Customer in Brokerage','Amount due from customers for fees and charges arising from transactions related to the entity\'s brokerage activities and operations.'),(2570,'ReceivablesHeldForSaleAmount',1,2,1,'Accounts and Financing Receivables, Held-for-Sale','Amount, before valuation allowance, of accounts and financing receivables held for sale.'),(2571,'ReceivablesNetCurrent',1,2,1,'Receivables, Net, Current','The total amount due to the entity within one year of the balance sheet