ation charged to expense in oil- and gas-producing activities.'),(2697,'ResultsOfOperationsDepreciationDepletionAndAmortizationAndValuationProvisions',1,2,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, Depreciation, Depletion, Amortization, and Valuation Provision','Amount of depreciation, depletion, amortization, and valuation provision charged to expense in oil- and gas-producing activities.'),(2698,'ResultsOfOperationsDryHoleCosts',1,2,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, Dry Hole Cost','Amount of dry hole cost charged to expense in oil- and gas-producing activities.'),(2699,'ResultsOfOperationsExpenseOther',1,2,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, Expense, Other','Amount of cost charged to expense in oil- and gas-producing activities classified as other.'),(2700,'ResultsOfOperationsExplorationExpense',1,2,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, Exploration Cost','Amount of exploration cost charged to expense in oil- and gas-producing activities. Includes, but is not limited to, geological, geophysical, and dry hole costs.'),(2701,'ResultsOfOperationsGeneralAndAdministrativeRelatedToOilAndGasProducingActivities',1,2,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, General and Administrative Expense','Amount of general and administrative costs charged to expense in oil- and gas-producing activities.'),(2702,'ResultsOfOperationsImpairmentOfOilAndGasProperties',1,2,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, Impairment','Amount of impairment for oil and gas properties charged to expense in oil- and gas-producing activities.'),(2703,'ResultsOfOperationsIncomeBeforeIncomeTaxes',1,1,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, before Income Tax Expense (Benefit)','Amount, before income tax expense (benefit), of result of operation in oil- and gas-producing activities. Excludes corporate overhead and interest costs.'),(2704,'ResultsOfOperationsIncomeTaxExpense',1,2,2,'Oil and Gas, Result of Operation, Income Tax Expense (Benefit)','Amount of income tax expense (benefit) in oil- and gas-producing activities.')