eceivable','Amount of accounts receivable that are delinquent at the end of the reporting period.'),(2713,'RetailLandSalesEstimatedCostOfMajorImprovementsFifthYear',1,2,2,'Retail Land Sale, Estimated Cost of Major Improvement, Year Five','Estimated cost of expenditure for improvement for each major area from which retail land sale was made during fifth fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach).'),(2714,'RetailLandSalesEstimatedCostOfMajorImprovementsFirstYear',1,2,2,'Retail Land Sale, Estimated Cost of Major Improvement, Year One','Estimated cost of expenditure for improvement for each major area from which retail land sale was made during next fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach).'),(2715,'RetailLandSalesEstimatedCostOfMajorImprovementsFourthYear',1,2,2,'Retail Land Sale, Estimated Cost of Major Improvement, Year Four','Estimated cost of expenditure for improvement for each major area from which retail land sale was made during fourth fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach).'),(2716,'RetailLandSalesEstimatedCostOfMajorImprovementsSecondYear',1,2,2,'Retail Land Sale, Estimated Cost of Major Improvement, Year Two','Estimated cost of expenditure for improvement for each major area from which retail land sale was made during second fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach).'),(2717,'RetailLandSalesEstimatedCostOfMajorImprovementsThirdYear',1,2,2,'Retail Land Sale, Estimated Cost of Major Improvement, Year Three',