e portion of unrecorded unconditional purchase obligation to be paid in fourth fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach). Includes, but is not limited to, lease not yet commenced.'),(3048,'UnrecordedUnconditionalPurchaseObligationBalanceOnSecondAnniversary',1,1,1,'Unrecorded Unconditional Purchase Obligation, to be Paid, Year Two','Amount of fixed and determinable portion of unrecorded unconditional purchase obligation to be paid in second fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach). Includes, but is not limited to, lease not yet commenced.'),(3049,'UnrecordedUnconditionalPurchaseObligationBalanceOnThirdAnniversary',1,1,1,'Unrecorded Unconditional Purchase Obligation, to be Paid, Year Three','Amount of fixed and determinable portion of unrecorded unconditional purchase obligation to be paid in third fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach). Includes, but is not limited to, lease not yet commenced.'),(3050,'UnrecordedUnconditionalPurchaseObligationBalanceOnFirstAnniversary',1,1,1,'Unrecorded Unconditional Purchase Obligation, to be Paid, Year One','Amount of fixed and determinable portion of unrecorded unconditional purchase obligation to be paid in next fiscal year following current fiscal year. Excludes interim and annual periods when interim periods are reported from current statement of financial position date (rolling approach). Includes, but is not limited to, lease not yet commenced.'),(3051,'UnrecordedUnconditionalPurchaseObligationImputedInterest',1,2,1,'Unrecorded Unconditional Purchase Obligation, Imputed Interest','If disclosed, the amount of imputed interest necessary to reduce an unconditional purchase obligation to present value on an unrecorded unconditional purchase obligation.'),(3052,'UnrecordedUnconditionalPurchaseObligationPurchases',1,2,2,'Unrecorded Unconditional Purchase Obligation, Purchases','The amount purchased during the period under an unrecorded unconditional purchase obligation (for example, under the take-or-pay or throughput contract).'),(3053,'UnrecoveredCostsForPurchasedGasAmount',1,2,1,'Unrecovered Costs for Purchased Gas Amount','Discloses the amount of unrecovered costs for purchased gas.'),(3054,'UnrecoveredProductionCostsExcessOfEstimatedAverageUnitCost',1,2,1,'Unrecovered Production Costs, Excess of Estimated Average Unit Cost','The aggregate amount of manufacturing or production costs and any related deferred costs (for example, initial tooling costs) that exceeds the aggregate estimated cost of all in-process and delivered units on the basis of the estimated average cost of all units expected to be produced under long-term contracts and programs not yet complete.'),(3055,'UnrecoveredProductionCostsExcessUnrecoverableUnderExistingFirmOrders',1,2,1,'Unrecovered Production Costs, Excess Unrecoverable under Existing Firm Orders','The portion of the aggregate amount of manufacturing or production costs and any related deferred costs (for example, initial tooling costs) that exceeds the aggregate estimated cost of all in-process and delivered units on the basis of the estimated average cost of all units expected to be produced under long-term contracts and programs not yet complete, which would not be absorbed in cost of sales based on existing firm orders at the latest balance sheet date.'),(3056,'UnregulatedOperatingRevenue',1,1,2,'Unregulated Operating Revenue','The amount of unregulated operating revenues recognized during the period.'),(3057,'UnsecuredDebtCurrent',1,1,1,'Unsecured Debt, Current','Carrying value as of the balance sheet date of the portion of long-term, uncollateralized debt obligations due within one year or the normal operating cycle, if longer.'),(3058,'UnsecuredDebt',1,1,1,'Unsecured Debt','Including the current and noncurrent portions, carrying value as of the balance sheet date of uncollateralized debt obligations (with maturities initially due after one year or beyond the operating cycle if longer).'),(3059,'UnsecuredLongTermDebt',1,1,1,'Unsecured Long-Term Debt, Noncurrent','Carrying value as of the balance sheet date of uncollateralized debt obligation (with maturities initially due after one year or beyond the operating cycle if longer), excluding current portion.'),(3060,'UnsolicitedTenderOfferCosts',1,2,2,'Unsolicited Tender Offer Costs','Costs incurred in connection with an unsolicited tender offer (one where the Entity being sought has not requested the offer). These would include costs relating to evaluation and dissemination of information regarding an unsolicited tender offer. A tender offer is a broad solicitation by an Entity or a third party to purchase a substantial percentage of another entity\'s shares or units for a limited period of time. The offer is at a fixed price, usually at a premium over the current market price, and is contingent on shareholders\' tendering a fixed number of their shares or units.'),(3061,'UnusualOrInfrequentItemNetOfInsuranceProceeds',1,2,2,'Unusual or Infrequent Item, or Both, Net of Insurance Proceeds','Amount, after deduction of insurance proceeds, of loss recognized in the income statement for an event or transaction that is unusual in nature or infrequent in occurrence, or both.'),(3062,'UnusualOrInfrequentItemInsuranceProceeds',1,1,2,'Unusual or Infrequent Item, or Both, Insurance Proceeds','Amount of insurance proceeds for an event or transaction that is unusual in nature or infrequent in occurrence, or both.'),(3063,'PaymentsForOperatingActivities',1,1,2,'Payments for Operating Activities','Total amount of cash paid for operating activities during the current period.'),(3064,'UtilitiesOperatingExpense',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense','Amount of operating expense of regulated operation.'),(3065,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseDepreciationAndAmortization',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Depreciation and Amortization','Amount of operating expense for depreciation and amortization of regulated operation.'),(3066,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseGasAndPetroleumPurchased',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Gas and Petroleum Purchased','Amount of operating expense for purchased gas and petroleum of regulated operation.'),(3067,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseImpairments',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Impairments','Amount of operating expense for impairments of regulated operation.'),(3068,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseMaintenance',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Maintenance','Amount of operating expense for routine plant maintenance and repairs of regulated operation.'),(3069,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseMaintenanceAndOperations',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Maintenance and Operations','Amount of operating expense for routine plant maintenance, repairs and operations of regulated operation.'),(3070,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseOperations',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Operations','Amount of operating expense for routine operations of regulated operation.'),(3071,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseOther',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Other','Amount of other operating expense of regulated operation.'),(3072,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseProductsAndServices',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Products and Services','Amount of operating expense for products and services of regulated operation.'),(3073,'UtilitiesOperatingExpensePurchasedPower',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Purchased Power','Amount of operating expense for purchased power of regulated operation.'),(3074,'UtilitiesOperatingExpensePurchasedPowerUnderLongTermContracts',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Purchased Power under Long-Term Contracts','Amount of operating expense for purchased power procured under arrangements extending beyond one year or the normal operating cycle, if longer, by regulated operation.'),(3075,'UtilitiesOperatingExpenseTaxes',1,2,2,'Utilities Operating Expense, Taxes','Amount of operating expense for taxes other than income taxes of regulated operation.'),(3076,'PublicUtilitiesPropertyPlantAndEquipmentAmountOfIndirectDisallowanceOfCostsOfRecentlyCompletedPlants',1,2,2,'Public Utilities, Property, Plant and Equipment, Amount of Indirect Disallowance of Costs of Recently Completed Plants','The amount of indirect disallowance of costs of a recently completed plant. When it becomes probable that part of the cost of a recently completed plant will be disallowed for rate-making purposes and a reasonable estimate of the amount of the disallowance can be made, the estimated amount of the probable disallowance is deducted from the reported cost of the plant and recognized as a loss. If part of the cost is explicitly, but indirectly, disallowed (for example, by an explicit disallowance of return on investment on a portion of the plant), an equivalent amount of cost is deducted from the reported cost of the plant and recognized as a loss.'),(3077,'PublicUtilitiesInventory',1,2,1,'Public Utilities, Inventory','The period end amount for a type of inventory held by the utility in a schedule of inventories.'),(3078,'ValuationAllowanceForImpairmentOfRecognizedServicingAssetsBalance',1,1,1,'Valuation Allowance for Impairment of Recognized Servicing Assets, Balance','Reflects the estimated amount of impairment as of the balance sheet date of recognized servicing assets that are being amortized in proportion to and over the period of estimated net servicing income or loss.'),(3079,'ValuationAllowanceForImpairmentOfRecognizedServicingAssetsPeriodIncreaseDecrease',1,NULL,2,'Valuation Allowance for Impairment of Recognized Servicing Assets, Period Increase (Decrease)','The net increase (decrease) in the valuation allowance for servicing assets subsequently measured using the amortization method.'),(3080,'ValuationAllowanceForImpairmentOfRecognizedServicingAssetsProvisionsRecoveries',1,1,2,'Valuation Allowance for Impairment of Recognized Servicing Assets, Additions (Deductions) for Expenses (Recoveries)','Amount of increase (decrease) in the valuation allowance for impairment of contract to service financial assets under which the benefits of servicing are expected to more than adequately compensate the servicer from expenses (recoveries) recognized.'),(3081,'ValuationAllowanceForImpairmentOfRecognizedServicingAssetsSalesAndDisposals',1,2,2,'Valuation Allowance for Impairment of Recognized Servicing Assets, Sales and Disposals','Reduction in valuation allowance of servicing assets based on sales and disposals.'),(3082,'ValuationAllowancesAndReservesAdjustments',1,1,2,'SEC Schedule, 12-09, Valuation Allowances and Reserves, Increase (Decrease) Adjustment','Amount of increase (decrease) in valuation and qualifying accounts and reserves from adjustment.'),(3083,'ValuationAllowancesAndReservesBalance',1,1,1,'SEC Schedule, 12-09, Valuation Allowances and Reserves, Amount','Amount of valuation and qualifying accounts and reserves.'),(3084,'ValuationAllowancesAndReservesChargedToCostAndExpense',1,1,2,'SEC Schedule, 12-09, Valuation Allowances and Reserves, Additions, Charge to Cost and Expense','Amount of increase in valuation and qualifying accounts and reserves from charge to cost and expense.'),(3085,'ValuationAllowancesAndReservesChargedToOtherAccounts',1,1,2,'SEC Schedule, 12-09, Valuation Allowances and Reserves, Additions, Charge to Other Account','Amount of increase in valuation and qualifying accounts and reserves from charge to accounts other than cost and expense.'),(3086,'ValuationAllowancesAndReservesDeductions',1,2,2,'SEC Schedule, 12-09, Valuation Allowances and Reserves, Deduction','Amount of decrease in valuation and qualifying accounts and reserves.'),(3087,'ValuationAllowancesAndReservesRecoveries',1,1,2,'SEC Schedule, 12-09, Valuation Allowances and Reserves, Addition, Recovery','Amount of increase in valuation and qualifying accounts and reserves from recovery of amount previously written off or reestablishment of reserve previously utilized.'),(3088,'ValuationAllowancesAndReservesReservesOfBusinessesAcquired',1,1,2,'SEC Schedule, 12-09, Valuation Allowances and Reserves, Business Acquired','Amount of increase in valuation and qualifying accounts and reserves from business combination.'),(3089,'ValueAddedTaxReceivable',1,2,1,'Value Added Tax Receivable','Carrying amount as of the balance sheet date of value added taxes due either from customers arising from sales on credit terms, or as previously overpaid to tax authorities.'),(3090,'ValueOfBusinessAcquiredVOBA',1,2,1,'Present Value of Future Insurance Profits, Net','Amount, after accumulated amortization, of present value of future profits of insurance contract acquired in business combination.'),(3091,'VariableInterestEntityOwnershipPercentage',2,NULL,2,'Variable Interest Entity, Qualitative or Quantitative Information, Ownership Percentage','Percentage of the Variable Interest Entity\'s (VIE) voting interest owned by (or beneficial interest in) the reporting entity (directly or indirectly).'),(3092,'WarehouseAgreementBorrowings',1,1,1,'Warehouse Agreement Borrowings','Carrying value as of the balance sheet date of the outstanding short-term borrowings under a revolving line of credit used by mortgage bankers to finance the origination or purchase of loans.'),(3093,'OtherInventoryWarehouse',1,2,1,'Other Inventory, Warehouse, Gross','Gross amount of merchandise, goods, commodities, or supplies held by the entity in a building or part of a building for future sale.'),(3094,'WarrantsAndRightsOutstanding',1,1,1,'Warrants and Rights Outstanding','Value of outstanding derivative securities that permit the holder the right to purchase securities (usually equity) from the issuer at a speci