ed Compensation Share-Based Arrangements, Liability, Current','Aggregate carrying value as of the balance sheet date of the liabilities for stock option plans and other equity-based compensation arrangements payable within one year (or the operating cycle, if longer).'),(3569,'GeneralAndAdministrativeCostsInInventoryAmountIncurred',1,2,1,'General and Administrative Costs in Inventory, Amount Incurred','Aggregate amount of general and administrative costs incurred in each period and charged to inventory.'),(3570,'GeneralAndAdministrativeCostsInInventoryAmountRemaining',1,2,1,'General and Administrative Costs in Inventory, Amount Remaining','Actual or estimated amount of general and administrative costs remaining in inventory.'),(3571,'IncomeLossFromContinuingOperationsBeforeIncomeTaxesMinorityInterestAndIncomeLossFromEquityMethodInvestments',1,1,2,'Income (Loss) from Continuing Operations before Equity Method Investments, Income Taxes, Noncontrolling Interest','Amount of income (loss) from continuing operations before deduction of income tax expense (benefit) and income (loss) attributable to noncontrolling interest, and addition of income (loss) from equity method investments.'),(3572,'OtherDeferredCreditsCurrent',1,1,1,'Other Deferred Credits, Current','Amount of unearned revenue or income classified as other, expected to be taken into income within one year or the normal operating cycle, if longer.'),(3573,'OtherDeferredCompensationArrangementsLiabilityCurrent',1,1,1,'Other Deferred Compensation Arrangements, Liability, Current','Amount of the liabilities, classified as other, for deferred compensation arrangements payable within one year or the operating cycle, if longer.'),(3574,'AdvancesReceivedOnGovernmentContractsNotNettedAgainstAccountsReceivable',1,1,1,'Advances Received on Government Contracts, Not Netted Against Accounts Receivable','Advances received on government contracts that are not offset against receivables because they cannot be definitely regarde