ted not to be offset. Excludes liabilities not subject to a master netting arrangement.'),(3627,'ShortDurationContractsDiscountedLiabilitiesAmount',1,1,1,'Short-Duration Contracts, Discounted Liabilities, Amount','The carrying amount as of the balance sheet date of loss reserves carried at present value.'),(3628,'ShortDurationContractsDiscountedLiabilitiesDiscountRate',2,NULL,1,'Short-Duration Contract, Discounted Liability, Discount Rate','Discount rate used to obtain present value of liability for unpaid claim and claim adjustment expense for short-duration contract issued by insurance entity.'),(3629,'StatutoryAccountingPracticesPortionOfExcessRetainedEarningsNotTaxed',1,1,1,'Statutory Accounting Practices, Portion of Excess Retained Earnings Not Taxed','The amount of retained earnings as of the balance sheet date in excess of statutory unassigned surplus on which no income tax provisions have been made.'),(3630,'ParticipatingPoliciesAmountInForce',1,1,1,'Participating Insurance, Amount in Force','Amount of participating insurance in force.'),(3631,'ParticipatingPoliciesAsPercentageOfGrossInsuranceInForce',2,NULL,1,'Participating Insurance, Percentage of Gross Insurance in Force','Percentage of participating insurance contract to insurance contracts in force.'),(3632,'ParticipatingPoliciesAdditionalIncomeAllocated',1,2,2,'Participating Insurance, Additional Income Allocated','Amount of additional income allocated to policy holders whose contracts entitle them to a portion of the entity\'s earnings or surplus, paid through dividends.'),(3633,'PolicyholderDividendsRateOnPolicyEarnings',2,NULL,2,'Policyholder Dividends, Rate on Policy Earnings','The percentage of earnings allocable to participating policyholders based on earnings of such policies for payment of dividends.'),(3634,'UnusualOrInfrequentTaxEffect',1,2,2,'Unusual or Infrequent Item, or Both, Tax Effect','Amount of tax related to an event or transaction that is unusual in nature or infrequent in occurrence, or both.'),(3635,'GainLossOnDerivativeInstrumentsHeldForTradingPurposesNet',1,1,2,'Gain (Loss) on Derivative Instruments Held for Trading Purposes, Net','Aggregate net gain and losses (whether realized or unrealized) on all derivative instruments held for trading purposes whether or not settled physically.'),(3636,'EstimateOfCancellations',1,2,2,'Estimate of Cancellations','Estimates of cancellations for refundable service fees, if accounted for by analogy to FASB Statement No. 48.'),(3637,'InsuranceRecoveries',1,1,2,'Insurance Recoveries','The amount recovered from insurance. These recoveries reduce costs and losses that are reported as a separate line item under operating expenses.'),(3638,'GainLossOnSaleOfStockInSubsidiaryOrEquityMethodInvestee',1,1,2,'Gain (Loss) on Disposition of Stock in Subsidiary or Equity Method Investee','Amount of gain (loss) on sale or disposal of equity in securities of subsidiaries or equity method investee.'),(3639,'ServicingAssetAtFairValueOtherChangesInFairValue',1,2,2,'Servicing Asset at Fair Value, Other Changes in Fair Value','Amount of increase (decrease) from changes in fair value classified as other for a contract to service financial assets under which the benefits of servicing are expected to more than adequately compensate the servicer.'),(3640,'ServicingAssetAtFairValueOtherChangesThatAffectBalance',1,2,2,'Servicing Asset at Fair Value, Other Changes that Affect Balance','Amount of increase (decrease) in fair value from changes classified as other for a contract to service financial assets under which the benefits of servicing are expected to more than adequately compensate the servicer.'),(3641,'ServicingLiabilityAtFairValueOtherChangesInFairValue',1,1,2,'Servicing Liability at Fair Value, Other Changes in Fair Value','Amount of increase (decrease) from changes in fair value classified as other for a contract to service financial assets under which the estimated future revenues from contractually specified servicing fe