edStock',1,1,2,'Dilutive Securities, Effect on Basic Earnings Per Share, ESOP Convertible Preferred Stock','Amount of increase (decrease) to net income used for calculating diluted earnings per share (EPS), resulting from the assumed exercise of convertible preferred stock of an employee stock ownership plan (ESOP).'),(3973,'DilutiveSecurities',1,1,2,'Dilutive Securities, Effect on Basic Earnings Per Share','Amount of increase (decrease) to net income used for calculating diluted earnings per share (EPS), resulting from the assumed exercise stock options, restrictive stock units (RSUs), convertible preferred stock of an employee stock ownership plan (ESOP), and other dilutive convertible securities.'),(3974,'StockRedeemedOrCalledDuringPeriodValue',1,2,2,'Stock Redeemed or Called During Period, Value','Equity impact of the value of stock bought back by the entity at the exercise price or redemption price.'),(3975,'PaymentOfFinancingAndStockIssuanceCosts',1,1,2,'Payment of Financing and Stock Issuance Costs','The total of the cash outflow during the period which has been paid to third parties in connection with debt origination, which will be amortized over the remaining maturity period of the associated long-term debt and the cost incurred directly for the issuance of equity securities.'),(3976,'InterestOnConvertibleDebtNetOfTax',1,1,2,'Interest on Convertible Debt, Net of Tax','Amount, after tax, of interest recognized on convertible debt instrument excluding interest on principal required to be paid in cash.'),(3977,'ConvertiblePreferredDividendsNetOfTax',1,1,2,'Convertible Preferred Dividends, Net of Tax','The after-tax amount of any dividends on convertible preferred stock.'),(3978,'NoncashContributionExpense',1,2,2,'Noncash Contribution Expense','Noncash charitable contributions made by the entity during the period.'),(3979,'IncomeTaxRefundsDiscontinuedOperations',1,2,2,'Income Tax Refunds, Discontinued Operations','The amount of cash received during the period 