e-Based Compensation Arrangement by Share-Based Payment Award, Options, Vested and Expected to Vest, Exercisable, Number','Number of fully vested and expected to vest exercisable options that may be converted into shares under option plan. Includes, but is not limited to, unvested options for which requisite service period has not been rendered but that are expected to vest based on achievement of performance condition, if forfeitures are recognized when they occur.'),(4013,'ShareBasedCompensationArrangementByShareBasedPaymentAwardOptionsVestedAndExpectedToVestOutstandingNumber',3,NULL,1,'Share-Based Compensation Arrangement by Share-Based Payment Award, Options, Vested and Expected to Vest, Outstanding, Number','Number of fully vested and expected to vest options outstanding that can be converted into shares under option plan. Includes, but is not limited to, unvested options for which requisite service period has not been rendered but that are expected to vest based on achievement of performance condition, if forfeitures are recognized when they occur.'),(4014,'ReceivablesFairValueDisclosure',1,2,1,'Receivables, Fair Value Disclosure','Fair value portion of receivables, including, but not limited to, trade account receivables, note receivables, and loan receivables.'),(4015,'ShareBasedCompensationArrangementByShareBasedPaymentAwardEquityInstrumentsOtherThanOptionsGrantsInPeriodIntrinsicValue',4,NULL,2,'Share-Based Compensation Arrangement by Share-Based Payment Award, Equity Instruments Other than Options, Grants in Period, Intrinsic Value, Amount Per Share','Per share or unit weighted-average intrinsic value of award granted under share-based payment arrangement. Excludes share and unit options.'),(4016,'ShareBasedCompensationArrangementByShareBasedPaymentAwardEquityInstrumentsOtherThanOptionsNonvestedIntrinsicValue',4,NULL,1,'Share-Based Compensation Arrangement by Share-Based Payment Award, Equity Instrument Other than Option, Nonvested, Intrinsic Value','Per share or unit weighted-average intrinsic value of nonvested award under share-based payment arrangement. Excludes share and unit options.'),(4017,'MineralPropertiesAccumulatedImpairment',1,1,1,'Mineral Properties, Accumulated Impairment','The accumulated decrease in the carrying value of the mineral properties as a result of adjustments in estimates of future income generating potential of the mineral property.'),(4018,'MineralPropertiesAccumulatedDepletion',1,1,1,'Mineral Properties, Accumulated Depletion','The accumulated decrease in the carrying value of the mineral properties as a result of mine or mineral production.'),(4019,'DerivativeNetHedgeIneffectivenessGainLoss',1,1,2,'Derivative, Net Hedge Ineffectiveness Gain (Loss)','Amount of gain (loss) from the ineffectiveness of the hedge.'),(4020,'StockRedeemedOrCalledDuringPeriodShares',3,NULL,2,'Stock Redeemed or Called During Period, Shares','Number of stock bought back by the entity at the exercise price or redemption price.'),(4021,'OtherAssetsFairValueDisclosure',1,2,1,'Other Assets, Fair Value Disclosure','Fair value portion of other assets.'),(4022,'LoansPayableFairValueDisclosure',1,1,1,'Loans Payable, Fair Value Disclosure','Fair value portion of contractual obligation to pay money on demand or on fixed or determinable dates.'),(4023,'LinesOfCreditFairValueDisclosure',1,1,1,'Lines of Credit, Fair Value Disclosure','Fair value portion of contractual arrangement with a lender under which borrowings can be made up to a specific amount at any point in time.'),(4024,'ConvertibleDebtFairValueDisclosures',1,1,1,'Convertible Debt, Fair Value Disclosures','Fair value portion of borrowing which can be exchanged for a specified number of another security at the option of the issuer or the holder, for example, but not limited to, the entity\'s common stock.'),(4025,'DividendsCommonStock',1,2,2,'Dividends, Common Stock','Amount of paid and unpaid common stock dividends declared with the form of settlement in cash, sto